ber"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="练习二-打印素数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#练习二-打印素数"><span>练习二：打印素数</span></a></h2>
<p>​	判断101~200之间有多少个素数，并输出所有素数。</p>
<p>备注：素数就是质数</p>
<p>代码示例：</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java" data-title="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">package</span> <span class="token namespace">com<span class="token punctuation">.</span>itheima<span class="token punctuation">.</span>test</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Test2</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
